<h3><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Online Instructor Requirements</span></h3>
<p><br />Master's degree or higher (unless otherwise stated in the job posting)<br /><br /> State residency where BYU-Idaho has an established hiring presence*</p>
<p>Online and/or classroom teaching experience preferred</p>
<p>Work experience in a related field preferred</p>
<p>Good standing in The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints</p>
<p>*At this time, BYU-Idaho has a hiring presence in the following states: Arizona, California, Colorado, Florida, Georgia, Idaho, Maryland, Nevada, New York, Oregon, Texas, Utah, Virginia, and Washington. We apologize for the inconvenience but due to the different state regulations and requirements it is hard to say when, or if, we will be able to establish a hiring presence in all 50 states. Unfortunately, we do not have a time frame for when new states will be added but updates will be made to the website at that time.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
